2. Hp ng ny (sau y gi tt l Hp ng), bao gm (i) bn Hp ng ny, (ii) iu
khon chung ca hp ng.
3. iu khon chung ca Hp ng (sau y gi tt l iu khon chung) c cng b
ti website chnh thc ca Bn B ti a ch ng dn http://www.qi.com.vn, c nim yt v
tham kho ti cc im giao dch ca Bn B, v do i din, nhn vin ca Bn B trc tip cung
cp cho Bn A trc khi hai bn k kt hp ng.
4. Hai Bn cam kt tun th iu khon chung v cc iu khon khc quy nh ti Hp
ng.
5. Bn B cam kt cung cp Dch v cho Bn A nh ghi ti Hp ng. Ngy bt u tnh
cc ca Dch v l ngy hai bn nghim thu v bn giao thit b.

(mt) nm (Thi hn). Khi Thi hn ca Hp ng kt thc, nu trong vng 30 (ba mi) ngy
trc khi ht hn m cc Bn khng c tha thun khc bng vn bn chnh thc th Hp ng
c t ng gia hn thm 01 (mt) nm v khng hn ch s ln t ng gia hn.
